   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Agreement between Kollauthis and Neilos who is aged x and has a scar on his left knee.  Neilos acknowledges that he has from her the loan of two hundred twenty-four [l. 5] drachmas in silver with interest at a drachma per mna per month and that of necessity he will pay to Kollauthis both [l. 10] principal and interest in the month of Pauni of the current year.  Kollauthis has the right of exaction from Neilos and from all his property.</ab>
